    <section id="about" class="container-fluid content-section text-center">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
          <h2>About Me</h2>
          <p>
            I'm everything from a software developer to a photographer, video editor, &amp; the like.
            I spend most of my time on a MacBook, learning, studying, working. I can build an entire software platform
            from nothing but little bits &amp; some planning.
          </p><br/>
          <p>
            I spent the first half of my life on the east coast, in New York &amp; later Maryland.
            After that I moved to Los Angeles, California. I spent a couple of years there &amp; later moved
            to this town nobody has ever even heard of. Well, life got boring &amp; I knew I wasn't going to spend my adolescence
            in that shitty town. So I made an app, made a deal with a record label through one of my ex's connections.
            So I made a couple of bucks off of that &amp; now I'm currently working on 2 more projects with some of my amigos in Brentwood, Los Angeles, CA.
          </p><br/>
          <p><i>Note: I'll come back to update this &amp; give it more detail after.</i></p>
        </div>
